itude<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Individuals Responsible: less than 5<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Arrests<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>None<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Warning<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of Social Privileges through 10\/11\/2024<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Decreased Social Privileges Fall 2024<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Required Third-Party Vendor<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Educational Assessment Fee<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hazing Prevention Education<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Alcohol Education<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Summer 2024 Description Zeta Psi new members were coerced or forced to perform acts of personal servitude. The chapter provided a common source of alcohol.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-722","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-9"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/722","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=722"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/722\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":723,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/722\/revisions\/723"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=722"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http